%E1%BA%A7n-M%E1%BA%A1c-D%C4%A9nh-Phu-s%E1%BB%A9-Nguy%C3%AAn/poem-Ken3H4rAzdLxHTACsMWXPQ">Tống thị thần Mạc Dĩnh Phu sứ Nguyên - 送侍臣莫穎夫使元</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-%E1%BB%A8c/author-KitWPFSrhqgQGR4JMcSBew">Nguyễn Ức</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%A5c-Du/Tri%C3%AAu-trung-th%E1%BB%91/poem-wqsfxh6uSr8iOp1gMLX_UA">Triêu trung thố - 朝中措</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%A5c-Du/author-6xOAUbKdWiBr-eAAn9zXQQ">Lục Du</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/U-nh%C3%A2n/poem-Dpws_IYIm_LPKzeJTUNyTA">U nhân - 幽人</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/V%E1%BB%8Bnh-M%E1%BA%A1c-tr%E1%BA%A1ng-nguy%C3%AAn/poem-ugArMJHyXe6R74OtG-UBWw">Vịnh Mạc trạng nguyên - 詠莫狀元</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/author-JHbQVfC53E2lRJL-xE616A">Nguyễn Khuyến</a>)<br></div>	</div>
